Package hash.int32

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IntHasher
    A 32-bit hash function.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    H2IntHasher
    Implements hash function from https://github.com/h2database/h2database.
    IdentityIntHasher
    Implements identity hash function.
    Murmur3IntHasher
    Implements Murmur3 32-bit finalizer (https://github.com/aappleby/smhasher/wiki/MurmurHash3)
    PhiIntHasher
    Multiply by the golden ratio and mix high bits into low bits.
    Prospector2RoundIntHasher
    Based on https://github.com/skeeto/hash-prospector#two-round-functions.
    Prospector3RoundIntHasher
    Based on https://github.com/skeeto/hash-prospector#three-round-functions.
